---
/**
 * Section 6: Pricing
 * Centered content, large price number with quiet fade reveal, single CTA.
 */
---

<section aria-label="Pricing" class="bg-brand-background py-section">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[50rem] px-lg text-center md:px-2xl">
    <!-- Section Heading -->
    <h2 data-reveal class="font-heading text-h2 font-medium uppercase leading-[0.95] tracking-[0.02em] text-brand-primary">
      One price. Everything included.
    </h2>

    <!-- Price -->
    <div data-reveal class="mt-4xl flex flex-col items-center text-center">
      <p class="font-heading text-display font-medium leading-none text-brand-primary" aria-label="$550 per person">
        $550
      </p>
      <p class="mt-sm font-body text-body-lg font-light text-brand-muted">
        per person
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Inclusion Text -->
    <p data-reveal class="mx-auto mt-3xl max-w-[44rem] font-body text-body-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-brand-primary">
      Eleven hours of curated wellness — yoga, Pilates, massage, acupuncture, meditation. Three chef-prepared meals. A private venue. A team handling every detail. Thirty women, one day, zero surprises.
    </p>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div data-reveal class="mt-3xl">
      <a
        href="/book"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-brand-primary px-3xl py-md font-body text-body font-light uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-brand-white transition-colors hover:bg-brand-primary-hover"
        style={`transition-duration: var(--duration-normal);`}
      >
        Reserve Your Place
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Small Print -->
    <p data-reveal class="mt-xl font-body text-small font-light text-brand-muted">
      Spaces are limited to 30 guests per event.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
